race.comment: ENTRUSTING (4) has needed the two starts this preparation and should be ready to fire. Three back he won a Sandown-Lakeside 70 over this distance and raced and Group and Stakes level following. Proven third-up and has plenty up the sleeve. The one to beat. COMPRESSING (6) resumed over 1600m at Moonee Valley and needed the outing. Won a 64 at his sole second-up outing and was last seen racing in Adelaide at Group level over longer trips. 2x winning rider John Allen is reunited and he'll he hitting the line. MARIOTA (11) improved again placing this distance range at Sale. Strips fitter and also has each way claims. Ditto FINALE (13) who was beaten narrowly at Mornington before a disappointing run at Moonee Valley (vet cleared). He was a big winner his only start here and steps up to this distance for the first time.
